Investment Services & Portfolio Management




Company Description


Founded in 2012, ShearLink Capital LLC is a hedge fund manager located in New York City. The firm brings a private equity approach to the public markets. They employ a disciplined process and conduct deep fundamental research to identify growth companies where their view differs from common market perception. The firm seeks to generate attractive risk-reward and the opportunity to compound returns over a multi-year holding period.






